import React from 'react'
import './header.css'
import { Header, Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react'

function SiteHeader() {
  return (
    <Segment clearing>
    <Header as='h2' floated='right'>
      Float Right
    </Header>
    <Header as='h2' floated='left'>
      Float Left
    </Header>
  </Segment>
  )
}

export default Header
